OL,3,CPolice warn holidaymakers about rogue
OL,4,CBristol Airport parking firms
OL,6,FPolice are urging holidaymakers to
OL,7,Fstick to official airport parking
OL,8,Fcompanies after they uncovered
OL,9,Fshocking abuses by operators near
OL,10,FBristol Airport.
OL,12,FAvon and Somerset Police carried out a
OL,13,Fday of action on 3 June targeting
OL,14,Funofficial parking firms, uncovering a
OL,15,Flitany of problems affecting
OL,16,Fcustomers' vehicles while they were
OL,17,Faway on holiday.
