OL,3,CPolice warn holidaymakers about rogue
OL,4,CBristol Airport parking firms
OL,6,FThe operation, conducted alongside
OL,7,FNorth Somerset Council, the
OL,8,FImmigration Enforcement Team and the
OL,9,FMotor Insurance Bureau, found that
OL,10,Fsome customers' cars had been involved
OL,11,Fin parking and driving offences,
OL,12,Fdriven by suspected uninsured
OL,13,Findividuals, or returned in an
OL,14,F"undriveable or unroadworthy"
OL,15,Fcondition.
