OL,3,CPolice warn holidaymakers about rogue
OL,4,CBristol Airport parking firms
OL,6,FOfficers were forced to locate and
OL,7,Freturn 20 vehicles to their owners
OL,8,Fafter unofficial meet-and-greet
OL,9,Fcompanies failed to hand them back
OL,10,Fpromptly, leaving families waiting
OL,11,F"for hours" after landing at Bristol
OL,12,FAirport.
OL,14,FThere was also the discovery of
OL,15,Fcustomer car keys being transported in
OL,16,Fa highly insecure manner.
