OL,3,CPolice warn holidaymakers about rogue
OL,4,CBristol Airport parking firms
OL,6,FPolice found one vehicle being used to
OL,7,Fdrive around the area returning keys
OL,8,Fto customers, with dozens of keys
OL,9,F"piled up on the front seat and in the
OL,10,Ffootwell" leaving them at risk of
OL,11,Ftheft.
OL,13,FSgt Danielle Hardaway, one of the
OL,14,Fsenior officers involved in the
OL,15,Foperation, said: "We have had reports
OL,16,Fof cars being returned damaged or with
OL,17,Fexcess mileage and, in some cases,
OL,18,Fhave been driven by people who are
OL,19,Funinsured as well as being involved in
OL,20,Fdriving offences.
