OL,3,CPolice warn holidaymakers about rogue
OL,4,CBristol Airport parking firms
OL,6,F"In some cases, vehicles left in
OL,7,Fdangerous or obstructive positions in
OL,8,Flocal villages had to be towed away."
OL,10,FShe warned customers to "always choose
OL,11,Freputable parking operators, and to
OL,12,Fchoose them carefully, and if the
OL,13,Fprice seems too good to be true, then
OL,14,Fit often is."
OL,16,FBristol Airport chief executive David
OL,17,FLees welcomed the police operation
OL,18,Ftargeting what he described as "rogue
OL,19,Foperators".
