OL,3,CPolice warn holidaymakers about rogue
OL,4,CBristol Airport parking firms
OL,6,F"They are a nuisance to local
OL,7,Fcommunities and cause distress to
OL,8,Fcustomers who use them ` with many
OL,9,Fcompletely unaware of where their cars
OL,10,Fend up," he said.
OL,12,FThe police force has advised
OL,13,Fholidaymakers to look for approved
OL,14,Fbusinesses when choosing where to
OL,15,Fleave their vehicles whilst travelling.
